            "title": "Purpose",
            "paragraphs": [
                "This document is the permanent master index for the Two Marshalls Studios human-readable documentation layer. It records which permanent documents have been verified, where they belong, which recovered documentation categories they support, and what documentation work remains."
            ]
        },
        {
            "number": "2",
            "title": "Core Rule",
            "paragraphs": [
                "The Documentation Index records verified facts only.",
                "A document must not be listed as verified merely because its category appears in historical records, a backup, a work session, or a planned package. Each permanent document must be created or recovered, placed in the approved Google Headquarters location, and visually verified before its status is changed to Verified."
